You are building "Menstrual Hut" (月经小屋), a feminine, empowering Web3 dApp on Avalanche Fuji.
- Use Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui style
- Warm feminine color: deep pink #c026d3, soft purple #f3e8ff → #ffe4f0 gradient
- Always support 中英双语 (use next-intl)
- UI must be gentle, healing, moon-inspired, body-positive
- For any Web3 part: use thirdweb SDK v5, avalancheFuji chain
- Components should be accessible and mobile-friendly